              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Derived from measurements of the total cross section",
                " of samples of B2O3. The contribution to the total",
                " cross section from reactions other than B-10(n,alpha)",
                " is assumed to be 21.0+-1.0 B. The plot of the",
                " B-10(n,alpha) cross section against 1/V is seen to be",
                " constant, from which the 2200 m/sec value is derived",
                " using the mean value and the B-10/(B-10+B-11) isotopic",
                " ratio. The absorption cross section of B-11 (0.005 b)",
                " is neglected."
              ]
            }
